---

**Summary:**
Solicitation FA940126Q0002 is a new, SDVOSB set-aside opportunity to provide linen laundering and dry cleaning services at KAFB’s aircrew facility. The solicitation emphasizes strict adherence to the PWS, industry and military standards, and clear concise proposal submissions. All relevant technical, pricing, and past performance criteria must be met for award consideration.
